  scType: 1
  scDesc: Perpetually shoots 8 fast shards per sec at the nearest enemy within a
    moderate range, each dealing 0.04 HP damage.
  scCommentary: "I remember weaving this card right after killing the Ice Fairy of
    the Misty Lake. The air around me condensed, forming into ice shards two or three
    inches wide, and just floated until they melted. Anyway, mighty reliable one
    \u2014 when's the last time I set out not having this in hand? "
